  "prompt": "My car back glass has been broken, how can I claim United India insurance?",
  "response": "To claim insurance for your broken car back glass with United India Insurance, follow these steps:\n\n1. Immediate Actions:\n- Contact United India Insurance claim helpline\n- Note down your policy number\n- Get your vehicle's registration details ready\n\n2. Claim Process:\n- Call United India Insurance customer support\n- Inform them about the back glass damage\n- Request the specific claim procedure for glass damage\n\n3. Documentation Required:\n- Insurance policy document\n- Vehicle registration certificate (RC)\n- Driving license\n- FIR/Police report (if applicable)\n- Photographs of the damaged glass\n- Repair estimate from authorized garage\n\n4. Claim Filing Options:\n- Visit nearest United India Insurance branch\n- Call their customer care number\n- File claim online through their website\n- Use their mobile app\n\n5. Claim Settlement:\n- Submit all required documents\n- Get surveyor's assessment\n- Receive claim approval\n- Get glass repaired/replaced\n\nContact Information:\n- Toll-free number: 1800-118-8585\n- Website: www.unitedindia.com\n\nPro Tips:\n- File claim immediately\n- Keep all documents ready\n- Choose authorized repair center\n- Follow insurance guidelines precisely\n\nNote: Specific procedures might vary, so directly contact United India Insurance for precise instructions.",
